OL,3,CCalls for review into Storm Claudia
OL,4,Cafter parts of Wales devastated by
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,FWelsh politicians have called for an
OL,8,Furgent review into the impact of Storm
OL,9,FClaudia after flooding left homes and
OL,10,Fbusinesses wrecked.
OL,12,FThe storm hit the UK on Friday and had
OL,13,Fa "devastating" impact in Wales, where
OL,14,Fa major incident was declared.
OL,16,FDozens of people were rescued from
OL,17,Ftheir homes or evacuated in the town
OL,18,Fof Monmouth, in south-east Wales,
OL,19,Ffollowing severe flooding when the
OL,20,FRiver Monnow burst its banks.
