OL,7,FDuring this time, Natural Resources
OL,8,FWales issued four severe flood
OL,9,Fwarnings, after just under five inches
OL,10,Fof rain fell in five hours.
OL,12,FThe full scale of the damage is not
OL,13,Fyet known, but it is thought by the
OL,14,FWelsh Government that hundreds of
OL,15,Fhomes and businesses have been
OL,16,Faffected.
