OL,7,FSpeaking at First Minister's Questions
OL,8,Fon Tuesday, Darren Millar, leader of
OL,9,Fthe Welsh Conservatives, called for a
OL,10,F"rapid review" of the storm and its
OL,11,Fimpact.
OL,13,FHe said: "The scenes, of course, in
OL,14,FMonmouth were extraordinary, those
OL,15,Fwere the ones that captured the
OL,16,Fheadlines.
OL,18,F"The River Monnow overtopped the flood
OL,19,Fdefences, it swept right through the
OL,20,Fcentre of the town at a pace that
OL,21,Fnobody could have expected.
