OL,4,Cafter parts of Wales devastated by
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,F"Homes were inundated, elderly
OL,8,Fresidents had to be evacuated in the
OL,9,Fmiddle of the night, and, of course,
OL,10,Fentire businesses were left destroyed
OL,11,Fwith us being just weeks away from
OL,12,FChristmas.
OL,14,F"We've got to make sure that we learn
OL,15,Flessons from these events quickly," he
OL,16,Fadded.
