OL,4,Cafter parts of Wales devastated by
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,F"What assurances can you give that a
OL,8,Frapid review will now be undertaken
OL,9,Finto what's happened, and that speedy
OL,10,Faction will be taken to invest, as is
OL,11,Fnecessary, to improve those flood
OL,12,Fdefences and help this community,
OL,13,Fparticularly in Monmouth, to get back
OL,14,Fon its feet, given that it was that
OL,15,Fhardest hit?"
