OL,4,Cafter parts of Wales devastated by
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,FFirst Minister Eluned Morgan said: "We
OL,8,Fcan, and we do, try and prepare for
OL,9,Fsituations like this, but when you get
OL,10,Ffive inches of rain in five hours you
OL,11,Fget a situation that was much worse in
OL,12,FMonmouthshire than even the storms of
OL,13,FBert and Dennis.
OL,15,F"So, we didn't see that absolute
OL,16,Finundation and the impact it would
OL,17,Fhave, but there was as much
OL,18,Fpreparation as could have been
OL,19,Fpossible.
