OL,3,CCalls for review into Storm Claudia
OL,4,Cafter parts of Wales devastated by
OL,5,Cflooding
OL,7,F"Everybody gave all the warnings in
OL,8,Fadvance, and I'd like to put on record
OL,9,Fmy thanks to the emergency services
OL,10,Ffor their sterling work in relation to
OL,11,Fthis, but also to the communities,
OL,12,Fwho've absolutely come together, who
OL,13,Fare working together, and making sure
OL,14,Fthat they are responding.
OL,16,F"We review after every event," she
OL,17,Fadded.
